      • actionPerformed

        public void actionPerformed(java.awt.event.ActionEvent e)
        0.5 seconds passed, select the item.

        NOTE: This method does not cycle through the icons, it flashes the START_ICON, then the next icon, then the start again, then the next one in the list.

        ie., If the count is even, display icon 0; if not, display (icon / 2 + 1).

        Specified by:
        actionPerformed in interface java.awt.event.ActionListener
